<h3>[Girls Grade 4-9] Winter JO traveling volleyball tryout registration</h3>
<p>
  <span class="label label-important">New for winter!</span>
  For players looking to improve their volleyball game in the off-season, Lakeville Juniors will organize a USA Junior Olympic volleyball program for Lakeville South players.
</p>
<ul>
  <li>One or more teams per grade level (grade 4-9) with 8-10 players per team</li>
  <li>Evening practice with weekend tournament play</li>
  <li>USA Junior Olympic sanctioned</li>
  <li>Season runs December through April, with play to begin in January</li>  
  <li>Tryouts to be held in late October (date/site TBD)</li>
</ul>
<p>
  Need more information? Contact club director <%= mail_to JO_CLUB_DIRECTOR_EMAIL_ADDRESS, 'Denielle Johnson', :encode => 'hex' %> with questions.
  <%= link_to 'Pre-register', JO_TRYOUT_FORM_URL, :target => '_blank' %> to receive more info and notification when tryout dates/times become available. 
</p>
<p style="margin-top:20px;margin-bottom:40px;">
  <%= link_to 'Pre-register for South JO tryouts!', JO_TRYOUT_FORM_URL, :target => '_blank', :class => 'btn btn-primary btn-large' %>
</p>

<h3>[Girls Grade 1-5] Fall 2013 in-house volleyball league registration!</h3>
<p>
  <span class="label label-important">Registration open!</span>
	Registration is now available for fall in-house volleyball. We would love to have you playing volleyball with us again! 
	You may <%= link_to 'register online now', new_registration_path %>, or a PDF version of the registration is available for <%= link_to 'download', 'fall.2013.inhouse.flyer.pdf', :target => '_blank' %>.
</p>
<p>
	Our in-house volleyball league is an instructional league for players in grades 1-5. 
  We'll host a beginner session for grades 1-3 and an intermediate session for grades 3-5.
  Players are placed on teams of 7-12 players for skill instruction and play. 
  Each date includes individual volleyball instruction, team practice, and game competition, with the final date being round-robin tournament play. 
  Players are instructed by Lakeville North/South high school team players and volunteer parent coaches, under the supervision of Lakeville Juniors head coaches.
  In-house volleyball is open to all, regardless of attendance area. 
</p>
<p><%= league_when_and_where_grid(false).html_safe %></p>

<h3>[12-and-under] Lakeville South Fall Traveling rosters</h3>
<p>
  Thank you to all the girls who tried our for our fall traveling teams. 
  We had over 50 players trying out for our grade 3-6 teams. 
  Players who did not make a team are eligible to attend August practice with our teams for volleyball skills training. 
  The cost is $40 per player for four sessions. 
  You may email <%= mail_to 'starkey77@charter.net', 'Penny Starkey', :encode => 'hex' %> to reserve your spot. 
  The first practice will be <strong>Monday Aug 19 from 700-830p</strong> at LSHS-Performance gym. 
</p>
<p>
  View the Fall 2013 fall traveling <%= link_to "calendar", 'http://lakevillejuniors.com/calendar' %>.
</p>

